{"tid":920930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市長偏心電動滑板車 紐約市議會立法頭痛","createTime":"2018-11-29T07:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T08:49:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8edd8a04c2ceb197469a245dfc2c6623aeeb17","tid":920930,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）紐約市議會周三推出四項草案，欲使電動滑板車和電動單車可合法在路上行駛。市長白思豪（Bill de Blasio）支持電動滑板車，但認為電動單車是交通混亂源頭，反對立場強硬，立法之路艱辛。<br />\n紐約市目前允許電動輔助單車，禁止不需踩踏板就能移動的全電動單車。市議會欲推出法案，使電動滑板車和電動單車皆能合法上路，滑板車限速每小時最高15英里，電動單可以全靠電動摩打移動，但仍必須安裝踏板，最高限速20英里。<br />\n此外，因應明年4月紐約地鐵L線關閉15個月進行整修，草案計畫沿L線試行城市共享電動滑板車，以每分鐘計費，沒有特定取車或還車據點，全靠App搜尋與登出。<br />\n在紐約，使用電動單車的人士，以外賣員和收入較低的勞工為主；而電動滑板車則多為年輕富裕居民使用，兩種交通工具背後其實涉貧富問題。為避免觸動政治神經，市議會的草案中還計畫撥款，補助電動單車車主改裝車輛至合法規格，務求使電動單車也能合法。<br />\n白思豪去年稱電動單車是「真正的危險」，要求警方加強執法。市長發言人斯坦（Seth Stein）表示，根據現行州法和市法，電動滑板車上路屬違規，「但市長致力於創新」，作為交通策略的一部分，期待能合法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543467242_eb6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543467242_eb6e.jpg&h=0dbfa126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181129/58971696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58971696&d=WoLvZM8B45wHJ3cTJ3oPmNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=05035c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58971696&h=8be1856d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181129/58971696</a>"},{"pid":"84bf34b47c102d13a6986cc8c6042ad4a4589334","tid":920930,"uid":389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"個市長真係好有職業操守<br />\n<br />\n自己中意但反對"},{"pid":"b70903b5bc3ea762ff0f8f239c60e285aec96efd","tid":920930,"uid":190328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"84bf34b47c102d13a6986cc8c6042ad4a4589334","tid":920930,"uid":389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"個市長真係好有職業操守<br />\n<br />\n自己中意但反對"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"佢偏心滑板車 所以反對單車喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6201833aafff712a4af83098770f47ff6f08f18f","tid":920930,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"單車可以載貨, 可以作為生財工具<br />\n滑板車連手抽袋大d 都難拎, 要靠背囊<br />\n所以使用上單車會多d"},{"pid":"5b2923bbe780a86d28b7cdfd713d7aae0b1b492e","tid":920930,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b70903b5bc3ea762ff0f8f239c60e285aec96efd","tid":920930,"uid":190328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"84bf34b47c102d13a6986cc8c6042ad4a4589334","tid":920930,"uid":389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"個市長真係好有職業操守<br />\n<br />\n自己中意但反對"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"佢偏心滑板車 所以反對單車喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"見人係鬼佬就含定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d5e5ec20917c4aea75923a595d7956a6024151","tid":920930,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95259ed936baefac3dff680232f2d942b5dab68f","tid":920930,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}